    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a smooth engine and transmission that perform exactly as they did when it first rolled off the lot. For a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives like it just left the dealership, this is the ideal choice.",
      "price": 49500.0,
